         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">17/9/96. ¶  ¶ Your brother, dear Mr French, undertook to convey to you my ¶  ¶ advise, not to miss the rare chance of securing a multitude of ¶  ¶ Acianthus ¶  ¶ caudotus. It will be in your own inter...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">96.09.17</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Charles<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>H.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>French</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M76, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>While the addressee is uncertain and might be Charles H. French's brother George, if M wished to give advice to the latter, he would surely have done so orally and not by letter since George was his<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>private<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>servant, whereas Charles H. French<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>had left the herbarium in July 1895 and was permanently employed in the Department of Agriculture as assistant to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>his father,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Government Entomologist.</p>
               </note>17/9/96.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your brother, dear Mr French, undertook to convey to you my<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>advise, not to miss the rare chance of securing a multitude of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Acianthus<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>caudotus. It will be in your own interest, as the specimens will all be sent out as collected by you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Very regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Acianthus caudotus</p>
         </div>
      </body>
